  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "As depth increases, pressure compresses everything. This preset channels that crushing force: very low fundamental, dense partial field, and a slow LFO modulating the filter cutoff downward — the sound darkens as if sinking. Effort is high but the filter is so low that the belt energy manifests as subharmonic rumble rather than brightness. The weight of a mile of water overhead.",
